# Generated schema artifacts (app/prisma, app/drizzle, app/database/migrations)
# are intentionally COMMITTED, not ignored: they carry a "generated, don't edit"
# header so diffs stay visible and CI is reproducible. Only an ORM's generated
# *client* is ignored.
.prisma/
**/generated/client/
